import React from 'react'
import {Box, Heading, Stack} from "@chakra-ui/react"

export const Train = () => {
  return (
    <Stack>
      <Heading>Train
        <Stack className='leftSide'>
          <Box>
            <Heading>Train Booking System</Heading>
          </Box>
        </Stack>
        <Stack className='rightSide'>

        </Stack>
      </Heading>
    </Stack>
  )
}
